## 📊 실전 예제: 도메인 모델링

### 예제: 언어 설계 시스템

```rust
#[derive(Debug, Clone)]
struct LanguageFeature {
    name: String,
    version: f32,
    description: String,
    is_stable: bool,
}

#[derive(Debug)]
struct LanguageRelease {
    version: f32,
    release_date: String,
    features: Vec<LanguageFeature>,
}

// 사용
let feature = LanguageFeature {
    name: String::from("Structs"),
    version: 5.0,
    description: String::from("데이터 구조화"),
    is_stable: true,
};

let release = LanguageRelease {
    version: 5.0,
    release_date: String::from("2026-02-22"),
    features: vec![feature],
};
```

### 구조체 관계도

```
LanguageRelease
├── version: f32
├── release_date: String
└── features: Vec<LanguageFeature>
    ├── name: String
    ├── version: f32
    ├── description: String
    └── is_stable: bool
```

